---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Help & Tutorial - LearningHub"
  description="Learn how to use LearningHub and access educational resources"
>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">‚Üê Back to LearningHub</a>
    </nav>
    <h1>Help & Tutorial</h1>
    <p>Learn how to use LearningHub effectively</p>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="help-content">
      <section class="help-section">
        <h2>What is This Website?</h2>
        <p>This is a gaming website disguised as an educational site. The homepage appears to be "LearningHub" but actually provides access to online games. The disguise allows you to quickly switch to educational-looking content if needed.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="help-section">
        <h2>Quick Reference</h2>
        <table class="reference-table">
          <tr>
            <th>Action</th>
            <th>How To</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Access Games</td>
            <td>Type "games" in the search bar</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Panic Button</td>
            <td>Press ESC key</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Star Topics</td>
            <td>Click star button on any topic page</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Get Help</td>
            <td>Type "help" in the search bar</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section class="help-section">
        <h2>How to Use</h2>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><strong>Access Games:</strong> Type "games" in the search bar to browse and play games by category (Action, Puzzle, Retro, Strategy). Click "Play Now" to open games in full-screen.</li>
          <li><strong>Panic Button (ESC):</strong> Press ESC at any time to instantly close games and redirect to an educational topic page. If you've starred a topic, it takes you there; otherwise, it picks a random topic.</li>
          <li><strong>Star System:</strong> Click the star button on any topic page to mark it as your panic destination. The panic button will always take you to your starred topic.</li>
          <li><strong>Stealth Mode:</strong> The site is designed to look like an educational platform. Games are hidden behind the "games" keyword and not visible on the homepage.</li>
          <li><strong>Game Library:</strong> Access games including 2048, Flappy Bird, Snake, Checkers, Sudoku, Tetris, Chess, and more.</li>
          <li><strong>Educational Facade:</strong> Browse subject categories (Math, Science, History, Literature, Technology, Geography) and topic pages that look completely legitimate.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  nav {
    margin: 0 auto clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 1rem);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: var(--max-content-width, min(1200px, 90vw));
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0 var(--spacing-unit, clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 1rem));
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  nav a {
    color: var(--accent, #0066cc);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1rem);
  }

  nav a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .help-content {
    max-width: min(900px, 90vw);
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0 var(--spacing-unit, clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 1rem));
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .help-section {
    margin: 0 0 clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem) 0;
    padding: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    background: white;
    border-radius: clamp(4px, 0.5vw, 8px);
    box-shadow: 0 clamp(2px, 0.3vw, 4px) clamp(4px, 0.6vw, 6px) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .help-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .help-section h2 {
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0 0 clamp(0.75rem, 1.5vw, 1rem) 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  }

  .help-section p {
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0 0 clamp(0.75rem, 1.5vw, 1rem) 0;
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2vw, 1.05rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .help-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .tutorial-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    margin: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem) 0 0;
  }

  .step {
    padding: clamp(0.75rem, 1.5vw, 1rem);
    background: #f9f9f9;
    border-left: clamp(3px, 0.4vw, 4px) solid var(--accent, #0066cc);
    border-radius: clamp(4px, 0.5vw, 8px);
  }

  .step h3 {
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0 0 clamp(0.5rem, 1vw, 0.75rem) 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.2vw, 1.3rem);
  }

  .step p {
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.8vw, 1rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .features-list {
    margin: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem) 0 0;
    padding-left: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    color: #000000;
  }

  .features-list li {
    margin: 0 0 clamp(0.75rem, 1.5vw, 1rem) 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2vw, 1.05rem);
  }

  .features-list li:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .features-list strong {
    color: #000000;
  }

  .reference-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem) 0 0;
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2vw, 1.05rem);
  }

  .reference-table th,
  .reference-table td {
    padding: clamp(0.75rem, 1.5vw, 1rem);
    text-align: left;
    border: clamp(1px, 0.1vw, 2px) solid #e0e0e0;
    color: #000000;
  }

  .reference-table th {
    background: var(--accent-bg, #f0f7ff);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000000;
  }

  .reference-table tr:nth-child(even) {
    background: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .reference-table tr:hover {
    background: #f0f7ff;
  }
</style>
